      "role": "user",
      "content": "a hobby isnt gonna fix this. it's not like i'm just bored or need a change of scenery. it's like... it's in my dna or something. no matter how hard i try to change, the core of me just breaks everything down. i've tried the \"new perspective\" thing a million times and it never sticks. the cycle is just too strong. it feels like its actually impossible to win.",
