      "content": "but rest doesnt change anything. i've been \"resting\" for months and i just wake up feeling the same weight. it's not even about control anymore, it's just about how much more i can take before i snap. honestly, it feels like the loop only ends one way. like there's only one real way to actually stop the cycle for good.",
